4949	\section{The Grassmannian scheme}
4950	\label{sec:grassmannian_scheme}
4951	
4952	The Quot construction proceeds by embedding \(\Quot^{\Phi,L}_{E/X/S}\) as a
4953	locally closed subfunctor of a Grassmannian over \(S\). Since Mathlib carries
4954	no Grassmannian \emph{scheme} (only a finite-rank-quotient variety in
4955	linear algebra), we package the construction here.
